Here’s the updated version of the HTML layout where all three sections —
✅ Workflow Cards,
✅ Important Notes, and
✅ Important Links —
are arranged side by side in a responsive layout.


---

✅ Desktop View Layout:

Left Column (70%) → Workflow Cards

Right Column (30%) → Important Notes + Important Links (stacked vertically)



---

✅ Full Updated HTML (Side-by-Side Layout)

